title: Unable to compile in Mac High Sierra 10.13.2
body_html:
I am using Mac OSX High Sierra 10.13.2, and I followed the instruction on the front page to install, but I failed when I run the setup.py using "MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET=10.9 CC=clang CXX=clang++ python setup.py install".( I also tried "MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET=10.13 CC=clang CXX=clang++ python setup.py install", but it doesn't seem to resolve the issue).

The errors that I am getting seem to be unknown type issue and they look like this:
"/Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer/Platforms/MacOSX.platform/Developer/SDKs/MacOSX10.13.sdk/usr/include/sys/resource.h:196:2: error:
unknown type name 'uint8_t'
uint8_t ri_uuid[16];"

I have attached the entire log here.
output.txt
